{
  "info": {
    "name": "Helwan Club - Packages & Privileges API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for managing privilege packages and staff privileges. This collection covers all endpoints related to:\n\n1. **Privilege Management** - View, grant, and revoke privileges\n2. **Privilege Packages** - Manage predefined sets of privileges\n3. **Staff Privilege Assignment** - Assign packages and individual privileges to staff members\n4. **Privilege Verification** - Check if staff has specific privileges\n5. **Activity Tracking** - View privilege-related activity logs\n\nAuthentication: All endpoints (except staff types) require Bearer token in Authorization header.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "📋 Staff Types",
      "description": "Get available staff types in the system",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get All Staff Types",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('staff_types', JSON.stringify(jsonData.data));",
                  "    console.log('Staff Types loaded:', jsonData.data);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/staff/types",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "staff",
                "types"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Retrieves all available staff types in the system (ADMIN, EXECUTIVE_MANAGER, DEPUTY_EXEC_MANAGER, etc.)\n\nNo authentication required.\n\n**Response Example:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"code\": \"ADMIN\",\n      \"name_en\": \"Administrator\",\n      \"name_ar\": \"مسؤول النظام\",\n      \"description_en\": \"Full system access\",\n      \"description_ar\": \"وصول كامل للنظام\",\n      \"is_active\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔐 Privileges",
      "description": "Manage and view system privileges",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get All Privileges",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('privileges', JSON.stringify(jsonData.data));",
                  "    console.log('Privileges loaded:', jsonData.count);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/staff/privileges?module=members",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "staff",
                "privileges"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "module",
                  "value": "members",
                  "disabled": true,
                  "description": "Optional: Filter by specific module (e.g., members, sports, finance)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Retrieves all available privileges in the system, optionally filtered by module.\n\n**Required Roles:** ADMIN (1) or EXECUTIVE_MANAGER (2)\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- `module` (optional): Filter by module name (members, sports, finance, etc.)\n\n**Response Example:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"count\": 45,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"members\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": 1,\n        \"code\": \"VIEW_MEMBERS\",\n        \"name_en\": \"View Members\",\n        \"name_ar\": \"عرض الأعضاء\",\n        \"module\": \"members\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": 2,\n        \"code\": \"CREATE_MEMBER\",\n        \"name_en\": \"Create Member\",\n        \"name_ar\": \"إنشاء عضو\",\n        \"module\": \"members\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Privileges by Module",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/staff/privileges?module=sports",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "staff",
                "privileges"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "module",
                  "value": "sports",
                  "description": "Filter by module name"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get privileges for a specific module (sports, members, finance, etc.)"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "📦 Privilege Packages",
      "description": "Manage privilege packages - predefined sets of privileges (CRUD operations)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get All Privilege Packages",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('packages', JSON.stringify(jsonData.data));",
                  "    if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.length > 0) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('package_id', jsonData.data[0].id);",
                  "    }",
                  "    console.log('Packages loaded:', jsonData.count);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/staff/packages",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "staff",
                "packages"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Retrieves all privilege packages defined in the system.\n\n**Response Example:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"count\": 3,\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"code\": \"MEMBER_MANAGER\",\n      \"name_en\": \"Member Manager\",\n      \"name_ar\": \"مدير الأعضاء\",\n      \"description_en\": \"Full member management access\",\n      \"description_ar\": \"وصول كامل لإدارة الأعضاء\",\n      \"is_active\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 2,\n      \"code\": \"SPORT_MANAGER\",\n      \"name_en\": \"Sport Manager\",\n      \"name_ar\": \"مدير الرياضات\",\n      \"description_en\": \"Sports management access\",\n      \"description_ar\": \"وصول إدارة الرياضات\",\n      \"is_active\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Privilege Package",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.id) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('new_package_id', jsonData.data.id);",
                  "    }",
                  "    console.log('Package created:', jsonData.data);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"FINANCE_MANAGER\",\n  \"name_en\": \"Finance Manager\",\n  \"name_ar\": \"مدير المالية\",\n  \"description_en\": \"Full financial management access\",\n  \"description_ar\": \"وصول كامل لإدارة المالية\",\n  \"privilege_ids\": [1, 2, 5, 10]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/staff/packages",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "staff",
                "packages"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Create a new privilege package.\n\n**Authorization:** ADMIN (staff_type_id=1) or EXECUTIVE_MANAGER (staff_type_id=2)\n\n**Request Body:**\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": \"PACKAGE_CODE\",              // Unique identifier (required)\n  \"name_en\": \"Package Name (English)\", // (required)\n  \"name_ar\": \"اسم الحزمة (عربي)\",      // (required)\n  \"description_en\": \"Description\",     // (optional)\n  \"description_ar\": \"وصف\",             // (optional)\n  \"privilege_ids\": [1, 2, 5, 10]       // Array of privilege IDs (required)\n}\n```\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Privilege package created successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 5,\n    \"code\": \"FINANCE_MANAGER\",\n    \"name_en\": \"Finance Manager\",\n    \"privileges_count\": 4\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Error Cases:**\n- 400: Missing required fields\n- 403: Insufficient privileges\n- 409: Package code already exists"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Package by ID",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('Package details:', jsonData.data);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/staff/packages/{{package_id}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "staff",
                "packages",
                "{{package_id}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get detailed information about a specific privilege package including all its privileges.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `packageId`: ID of the package\n\n**Response Example:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"code\": \"MEMBER_MANAGER\",\n    \"name_en\": \"Member Manager\",\n    \"name_ar\": \"مدير الأعضاء\",\n    \"description_en\": \"Full member management access\",\n    \"description_ar\": \"وصول كامل لإدارة الأعضاء\",\n    \"is_active\": true,\n    \"privileges_count\": 8,\n    \"privileges\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": 1,\n        \"code\": \"VIEW_MEMBERS\",\n        \"name_en\": \"View Members\",\n        \"name_ar\": \"عرض الأعضاء\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Privilege Package",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name_en\": \"Updated Member Manager\",\n  \"name_ar\": \"مدير الأعضاء المحدث\",\n  \"description_en\": \"Updated description\",\n  \"is_active\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/staff/packages/{{package_id}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "staff",
                "packages",
                "{{package_id}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Update a privilege package.\n\n**Authorization:** ADMIN (staff_type_id=1) or EXECUTIVE_MANAGER (staff_type_id=2)\n\n**Request Body (all fields optional):**\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": \"UPDATED_CODE\",            // Optional: change package code\n  \"name_en\": \"Updated Name\",         // Optional\n  \"name_ar\": \"الاسم المحدث\",        // Optional\n  \"description_en\": \"New desc\",      // Optional\n  \"description_ar\": \"وصف جديد\",      // Optional\n  \"is_active\": true,                 // Optional\n  \"privilege_ids\": [1, 2, 5]         // Optional: update privileges (replaces all)\n}\n```\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Privilege package updated successfully\",\n  \"data\": { /* updated package */ }\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Package Privileges",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"privilege_ids\": [1, 2, 3, 5, 10, 15]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/staff/packages/{{package_id}}/privileges",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "staff",
                "packages",
                "{{package_id}}",
                "privileges"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Update the privileges in a package (replaces all existing privileges).\n\n**Authorization:** ADMIN (staff_type_id=1) or EXECUTIVE_MANAGER (staff_type_id=2)\n\n**Request Body:**\n```json\n{\n  \"privilege_ids\": [1, 2, 3, 5, 10, 15]  // New array of privilege IDs\n}\n```\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Package privileges updated successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"package_id\": 1,\n    \"privileges_count\": 6,\n    \"privilege_ids\": [1, 2, 3, 5, 10, 15]\n  }\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Privilege Package",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/staff/packages/{{package_id}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "staff",
                "packages",
                "{{package_id}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Delete a privilege package.\n\n**Authorization:** ADMIN only (staff_type_id=1)\n\n**Restrictions:**\n- Cannot delete if package is assigned to active staff members\n- Will return 409 Conflict if deletion not allowed\n\n**Response on Success:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Privilege package deleted successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"deleted_package_id\": 1,\n    \"privileges_removed\": 8\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Error Cases:**\n- 403: Only ADMIN can delete\n- 409: Package is assigned to staff members\n- 404: Package not found"
          }
        },
        {
