                "privileges"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get all privileges included in a specific package.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `packageId`: ID of the package\n\n**Response Example:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"count\": 8,\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"code\": \"VIEW_MEMBERS\",\n      \"name_en\": \"View Members\",\n      \"name_ar\": \"عرض الأعضاء\",\n      \"module\": \"members\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 2,\n      \"code\": \"CREATE_MEMBER\",\n      \"name_en\": \"Create Member\",\n      \"name_ar\": \"إنشاء عضو\",\n      \"module\": \"members\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"
          }
        }
      ]
