            },
            "description": "Register a new staff member in the system.\n\n**Authorization Rules:**\n- Only ADMIN can register EXECUTIVE_MANAGER\n- ADMIN and EXECUTIVE_MANAGER can register other staff\n- DEPUTY_EXEC_MANAGER registrations require approval\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `first_name_en`: English first name (required)\n- `last_name_en`: English last name (required)\n- `first_name_ar`: Arabic first name (optional, defaults to English)\n- `last_name_ar`: Arabic last name (optional, defaults to English)\n- `national_id`: National ID (required)\n- `phone`: Phone number (required)\n- `address`: Address (optional)\n- `staff_type_id`: Type of staff (required)\n- `employment_start_date`: Start date YYYY-MM-DD (required)\n- `employment_end_date`: End date YYYY-MM-DD (optional)\n\n**Note:** Email is auto-generated as `staff.{national_id}@helwan-club.local` and initial password is set to the national_id."
